&lt;p&gt;Sphinx Defense is hiring a &lt;strong&gt;Software Systems Architect&lt;/strong&gt; to join our team and help shape the next generation of mission-critical software and systems supporting national security and space missions. As a growing defense technology company, we develop innovative software solutions that enable secure, resilient, and operationally relevant capabilities across complex mission environments.&lt;/p&gt;
