&lt;li&gt;Advocating for improvements to product quality, security, and performance that have a particular impact on your team and others&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supporting junior engineering talent with mentorship or technical guidance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interacting with customers and partners to help them integrate with our services&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Scale the services and solve interesting Space Communication challenges&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
