&lt;li&gt;Have extensive experience with Python, FastAPI, Postgres, AWS, Docker, Kubernetes, and Terraform*&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrable in-depth knowledge of at least one commercial cloud platform and its associated services&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Led the architecture, development, and building of backend services and APIs to ensure performance, security, and reliability&lt;/li&gt;
